**Test for Uniqueness:**
Before finalizing any visual opportunity or thematic observation, ask:
1. "Does this cite specific lyric content from THIS song?"
2. "Would I give this exact same visual hint for a different Christmas song?"
3. "Have I identified what makes THIS song's narrative/themes unusual or distinctive?"

